le Jan De Vos isn't actually a part of 4 Strings, he took up the name DJ 4 Strings and does all live performances in place of the actual group. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/4+Strings\">Read more on Last.fm</a>. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply."}}}